    "asOf": "2011-03-16",
    "date": "2011-03-28T19:44:19Z",
    "text": "Combat Act - Increases, as of the beginning of FY2011, the maximum monthly rates of: (1) hostile fire or imminent danger pay from $225 to $260; (2) hazardous duty pay from $250 to $260; and (3) the monthly family separation allowance from $250 to $285."
